<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@jblandford:matrix.org">Jonathan Blandford</a> reports</p>
<blockquote>
<p>An initial version of GNOME Crosswords was released and is looking for feedback. This is a simple crossword game for GNOME, with a planned Crossword Editor in the works. See the <a href="https://blogs.gnome.org/jrb/2021/11/18/introducing-gnome-crosswords/">release announcement</a> for more details.

